OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally spoke to
OL,8,Fresidents at a care home under threat
OL,9,Fof closure
OL,11,FResidents living in care homes facing
OL,12,Fclosure over fears of rising costs say
OL,13,Fthey would be "totally lost" if they
OL,14,Fwere to shut - urging the council to
OL,15,Fditch their plans.
