OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,FLancashire County Council is
OL,7,Fconsidering closing five care homes
OL,8,Fand five day centres across the
OL,9,Fcounty, which it says require
OL,10,Fsignificant investment to bring up to
OL,11,Fstandard.
OL,13,FBut a resident of one home, Woodlands
OL,14,FCare Home in Clayton-le-Moors, in
OL,15,FHyndburn, says it is not the view
OL,16,Fshared by those who live in them,
OL,17,Falong with the families and friends
OL,18,Fwho visit.
OL,20,FDorothy Devereux used to work in the
OL,21,Fvery building she now calls home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
