OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"I'm devastated, angry, frustrated,"
OL,7,Fshe said. "I would be totally lost if
OL,8,Fit closed, I just daren't think about
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,F"The thing is, where is everybody
OL,12,Fgoing to go? There's limited places
OL,13,Fprivately, and I don't want to go
OL,14,Fprivate, I don't see why I should.
OL,16,F"I worked hard, sold my bungalow, used
OL,17,Fvirtually all my money, it doesn't
OL,18,Fmake any sense."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
