OL,6,FDespite claims from the Reform-run
OL,7,Fcouncil that the building are outdated
OL,8,Fand require significant investments to
OL,9,Fbring them up to standard, Dorothy's
OL,10,Ffamily say they are not convinced.
OL,12,F"The CQC report from 2022 rates this
OL,13,Fhome as good," Dorothy's daughter Fran
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"There's no mention on that of any
OL,17,Fsafety issues with regards to the
OL,18,Fcondition of the building.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
