OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"The cost of moving people will in a
OL,7,Fmatter of months be greater than
OL,8,Finvesting in this purpose build,
OL,9,Fsingle story, this is priceless to
OL,10,Fmum."
OL,12,FMany of the 50 residents who live at
OL,13,FWoodlands have complex needs like
OL,14,Fdementia or other health conditions,
OL,15,Fwhich families say has added to the
OL,16,Falready anxious time.
OL,18,FJoanne Walker says she cannot even
OL,19,Fbring herself to tell her mum her home
OL,20,Fis under threat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
