OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"I know what it's going to do to her,
OL,7,Fand I can't stand breaking her heart,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"You just want to protect them, they
OL,11,Fcan't protect themselves, she can't
OL,12,Fbecause of her stroke.
OL,14,F"They shouldn't even be contemplating
OL,15,Fit, it's not human.
OL,17,F"I don't know where she's going to end
OL,18,Fup, there's nowhere around here, so
OL,19,Fshe'll know she's going to be be
OL,20,Ffurther away from me again, and the
OL,21,Fmove again...it does a lot of damage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
