OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"Especially when they are happy, this
OL,7,Fshould be where they can spend however
OL,8,Flong they've got, and not have to
OL,9,Fworry."
OL,11,FJoanne and Wayne say the home is loved
OL,12,Fby residents
OL,14,FSarah Smith, Labour MP for Hyndburn,
OL,15,Fis also urging the council not to go
OL,16,Fahead with the closures.
