OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"Where will these people go? I'm not
OL,7,Faware of a lot of spaces in care homes
OL,8,Fin Hyndburn and there's a big
OL,9,Ffinancial cost to families because it
OL,10,Fimpacts on their physical health and
OL,11,Fmental health and it often leads to
OL,12,Fthem being more likely to end up in
OL,13,Fhospital.
OL,15,F"So even if there might be super short
OL,16,Fterm savings directly to the council,
OL,17,Fthe wider health system will be
OL,18,Fimpacted."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
