OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,FThe council says it understands how
OL,7,Fvalued these services are, and
OL,8,Fstressed that no decisions have been
OL,9,Fmade.
OL,11,FCllr Graham Dalton, cabinet member for
OL,12,FAdult Social Care at Lancashire County
OL,13,FCouncil, said: "This review is part of
OL,14,FLancashire County Council's commitment
OL,15,Fto ensuring that the care we provide
OL,16,Fremains safe, high-quality, and
OL,17,Fsustainable for the years ahead.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
