OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"There has been a lot of
OL,7,Fmisinformation about this issue and I
OL,8,Fwould like to make it clear that no
OL,9,Fdecisions have been made about the
OL,10,Ffuture of any of these services.
OL,12,F"We are consulting to find out
OL,13,Fpeople's views to help us make the
OL,14,Fbest decision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
