OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"As part of the review we are also
OL,7,Fcarrying out new condition surveys on
OL,8,Fall our care homes and day centres so
OL,9,Fwe have the most up to date
OL,10,Finformation, and also considering the
OL,11,Fimpact of modernisation to be in-line
OL,12,Fwith CQC standards to determine
OL,13,Fwhether homes can be updated and if so
OL,14,Fwhat the cost would be. This will help
OL,15,Fform part of the wider assessment
OL,16,Fagainst the evaluation framework.
OL,18,F"It is also important to note that we
OL,19,Fare keeping the care market updated
OL,20,Fand have a good relationship in terms
OL,21,Fof collaboratively working.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
