OL,3,C'I'd be totally lost': Anger over
OL,4,Cproposals to close care homes
OL,6,F"I absolutely understand how deeply
OL,7,Fvalued these services are by those who
OL,8,Fuse them and their families as well as
OL,9,Fstaff and the wider community.
OL,11,F"We know that for many, these homes
OL,12,Fare not just buildings, they are
OL,13,Fplaces of comfort, familiarity and
OL,14,Fconnection.
OL,16,F"The consultation we are running is a
OL,17,Freally important opportunity for
OL,18,Fpeople to share their views and help
OL,19,Fshape the future of adult social care
OL,20,Fin our county."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
